('Sarah Chen', 'Bachelor of Business Administration', 'The business program at University Leads transformed my career prospects. The practical case studies and internship opportunities prepared me perfectly for the corporate world.', 5, 'https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1494790108377-be9c29b29330?w=200&q=80', true, 1),
