('Kumar Patel', 'Diploma in Engineering', 'Starting with the diploma program was the best decision. It built my confidence and gave me a solid foundation before I continued to the degree program.', 4, 'https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1472099645785-5658abf4ff4e?w=200&q=80', false, 6);
